Site : https://github.com/mazubieta/A-Star-Pathfinder
This is a demonstration tool using Python 2.6 and PyGame for the A* Pathfinding Algorithm.

After properly installing Python 2.6 and PyGame, to execute this demo:

$ python path.py

How to use it:

CTRL + left click - Place/Remove Start square

CTRL + right click - Place/Remove Goal square

SHIFT + left click - Place/Remove a Wall square (You can hold this down and move the cursor to place several 
						walls at a time)
ESCAPE - Clear the entire board

BACKSPACE - Clear path exploration, leaving Start, Goal and Wall squares

ENTER - Find the shortest path (in Verbose/Slow mode)

LEFT_ARROW - Find the shortest path